# Git

## log

* Show commits in ours branch but not in theirs

```bash
git log theirs..ours
```

## rebase

* Auto resolve conflicts using changes from working branch (current)

```bash
git rebase -Xtheirs master
```

* Resolve conflict using the changes from the target branch

```bash
git checkout --ours -- path/file
```

* Resolve conflict using the changes from the target working branch

```bash
git checkout --theirs -- path/file
```
